commitResults.messageTitle: Add more getTotalCost methods to Person
commitResults.messageBody:
Person now supports these getters:
getTotalCostPaid() (total costPaids of all the ActivityCosts associated
with the Person)
getTotalCostOwed() (total costOweds of all the ActivityCosts associated
with the Person)
getTotalCost() (total costPaids - total costOweds of all the
ActivityCosts associated with the Person)

Person no longer stores totalCost as a private variable. Get totalCosts
using the above getters instead.

commitResults.messageTitle: Fix infinite loop bug in getUserConfirmation
commitResults.messageBody:
getUserConfirmation would not ask the user to re-enter input if invalid
input was detected.

Let's ask the user to re-enter input every time invalid input is
detected to prevent an infinite loop.
